### Key Architectural Decisions Summary

| Decision | Choice | Rationale |
|---|---|---|
| Response model | Synchronous (base64 in response) | Simpler than Luma's polling; matches `openai-compatible` pattern at line 138-170 of its image model |
| Error structure | `{ error: { message, type, code } }` | Standard OpenAI-like structure, easy to handle |
| Provider options key | `'pixelart'` | Matches convention: lowercase provider name |
| Provider string | `'pixelart.image'` | Matches `{provider}.{modelType}` convention |
| maxImagesPerCall | 4 | Reasonable default for a fictional provider |
| Auth header | `Authorization: Bearer <key>` | Most common API key pattern |
| Unsupported features | `aspectRatio`, `seed`, `files`, `mask` | PixelArt only does text-to-image; these are all editing/variant features |
| Zod import | `from 'zod/v4'` | Matches the pattern used in Luma and other recent providers |

