## Implementation Plan: PixelArt AI Provider (`packages/pixelart/`)

### Overview

The PixelArt provider is an image-only provider for the Vercel AI SDK. It follows the Luma provider pattern for its overall structure (factory function, image model class, settings types, config files) but uses a simpler synchronous response model (similar to OpenAI-compatible providers) instead of Luma's asynchronous polling approach. The API returns base64-encoded images directly in the response body.

